    AtomicModelFactoryI, RTModelFactoryI, java.io.Serializable

    public class StandardRTAtomicHIOA_Factory
extends StandardRTAtomicModelFactory
    The class StandardRTAtomicHIOA_Factory defines a basic factory used when the instantiation protocol of a real time atomic HIOA model class does not modify the one defined in the class AtomicHIOA.

    Description

    White-box Invariant

     invariant       accelerationFactor > 0.0

    Black-box Invariant

     invariant       true        // no more invariant

    Created on : 2020-11-27

    Author:
    Jacques Malenfant
